OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FThe attack has renewed fears of a
OL,7,Fwider war in the Middle East that
OL,8,FIsrael and Iran-backed Hezbollah have
OL,9,Fcarefully avoided so far, despite a
OL,10,Fseries of attacks from both side
OL,11,Facross Israel's northern border since
OL,12,FHamas launched its October 7 attack.
OL,14,FThe Israeli military has declined to
OL,15,Fcomment on the pager blasts, and
OL,16,Fdetails on how the attack was executed
OL,17,Fare largely uncertain. Investigators
OL,18,Fhave not immediately said how the
OL,19,Fpagers were detonated.
