OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FITV News spoke to cybersecurity
OL,7,Fexperts about how the operation was
OL,8,Flikely to have been carried out and
OL,9,Fwhat implications it could have on
OL,10,Fglobal security in the future.
OL,12,FWhat caused the Lebanon pager blasts?
OL,14,FThe short answer is - we don't know
OL,15,Ffor sure, but cybersecurity expert
OL,16,FGerome Billois said he believes the
OL,17,F"most likely scenario appears to be
OL,18,Fthat the devices were sabotaged during
OL,19,Fdelivery".
