OL,6,F"This would allow for precise
OL,7,Ftargeting, as the incidents seem to be
OL,8,Flimited to specific groups, such as
OL,9,FHezbollah, and not widespread," he
OL,10,Fadds.
OL,12,FIntercepting and tampering with
OL,13,Fdevices during the delivery process is
OL,14,Fa known tactic used by intelligence
OL,15,Fservices, Mr Billois points out, as
OL,16,Frevealed by whistleblower Edward
OL,17,FSnowden in relation to the NSA
OL,18,Fplanting surveillance tools in routers
OL,19,Fand servers exported from the US.
