OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,F"Given the scale -several thousand
OL,7,Fdevices -it would require a
OL,8,Fmeticulously planned and highly
OL,9,Forganised effort to carry out such an
OL,10,Foperation undetected."
OL,12,FThe AR-924 pagers used by Hezbollah
OL,13,Fwere Gold Apollo branded. But the
OL,14,FTaiwanese company said the devices
OL,15,Fwere produced and sold by Budapest-
OL,16,Fbased company BAC, which is yet to
OL,17,Fcomment.
