OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FDr Andreas Krieg, Associate Professor
OL,7,Fat King's College London School of
OL,8,FSecurity, agreed the devices would
OL,9,Fhave to had been physically tampered
OL,10,Fwith.
OL,12,FHe suggests operatives must have
OL,13,F"infiltrated the supply chain" of the
OL,14,Fpagers, which were "likely sourced
OL,15,Fearlier this year from a company in
OL,16,FHungary producing pagers based on the
OL,17,Fblue prints of a Taiwanese company".
