OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FA former British Army bomb disposal
OL,7,Fofficer explained that an explosive
OL,8,Fdevice has five main components: a
OL,9,Fcontainer, a battery, a triggering
OL,10,Fdevice, a detonator and an explosive
OL,11,Fcharge.
OL,13,F"A pager has three of those already,"
OL,14,Fexplained the ex-officer, who spoke on
OL,15,Fcondition of anonymity because he now
OL,16,Fworks as a consultant with clients on
OL,17,Fthe Middle East. "You would only need
OL,18,Fto add the detonator and the charge."
OL,20,FCould the pagers' batteries have
OL,21,Foverheated?
