OL,6,FThe theory that overheating batteries
OL,7,Fas the result of malware has prompted
OL,8,Ffears expressed on social media that
OL,9,Fanyone's devices could be vulnerable
OL,10,Fto such an attack.
OL,12,FWhile Mr Billois says these concerns
OL,13,Fare "understandable", they "may be
OL,14,Foverstated".
