OL,6,F"This operation appears to have
OL,7,Ftargeted a very specific group, and
OL,8,Fthe complexity of the attack,
OL,9,Fincluding precise delivery
OL,10,Finterception and modification of
OL,11,Fhardware and software, suggests that
OL,12,Fthis is not something that could
OL,13,Feasily be replicated on a wide scale,"
OL,14,Fhe says.
