OL,6,F"However, it does highlight the need
OL,7,Ffor stronger security measures in the
OL,8,Fsupply chain and could lead to
OL,9,Fheightened scrutiny, especially for
OL,10,Fdevices used by high-risk groups or
OL,11,Findividuals, as well as more stringent
OL,12,Fsecurity protocols for hardware and
OL,13,Fsoftware vulnerabilities."
