OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FA pager, also known as a beeper, is a
OL,7,Fsmall battery-operated radio receiver
OL,8,Fthat when set off can display either
OL,9,Fnumeric or worded messages. They are
OL,10,Fnow used mostly in hospitals due to
OL,11,Freliable reception and because they're
OL,12,Fless likely to be affected by
OL,13,Finterference from medical equipment
OL,15,F"Hezbollah replaced mobile phones in
OL,16,FFebruary because they constituted such
OL,17,Fa vulnerability because they could be
OL,18,Fremotely hacked," says Dr Krieg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
