OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,F"Pagers are less vulnerable to
OL,7,Fsoftware hacking and are not traceable
OL,8,Fvia the internet. So the devices had
OL,9,Fto be fiddled with physically before.
OL,11,FHe said there were some "question
OL,12,Fmarks about the ethics of this sort of
OL,13,Fwarfare and spyfare" as the 5,000
OL,14,Fdelivered to Hezbollah were
OL,15,Fdistributed across relief
OL,16,Forganisations, civil societal groups
OL,17,Fas well as fighters.
