OL,12,Fdamage," Dr Krieg said. "And while
OL,13,Fthis looks very targeted, it was a
OL,14,Ffairly indiscriminate attack as it hit
OL,15,Fmostly civilians or potential fighters
OL,16,Fthat at the time of the strike were
OL,17,Fnot in active combat and therefore not
