OL,6,FHow long was this operation?JIt would
OL,7,Ftake a long time to plan an attack of
OL,8,Fthis scale, with experts hearing
OL,9,Festimates ranging anywhere between
OL,10,Fseveral months to two years.
OL,12,FThe sophistication of the attack
OL,13,Fsuggests that the culprit has been
OL,14,Fcollecting intelligence for a long
OL,15,Ftime, says Nicholas Reese, adjunct
OL,16,Finstructor at the Centre for Global
OL,17,FAffairs in New York University's
OL,18,FSchool of Professional Studies.
