OL,3,CWhat we know about the deadly pager
OL,4,Cexplosions in Lebanon
OL,6,FElijah J. Magnier, a senior political
OL,7,Frisk analyst, said he has had
OL,8,Fconversations with members of
OL,9,FHezbollah and survivors of Tuesday's
OL,10,Fpager attack. He said the pagers were
OL,11,Fprocured earlier this year.
OL,13,F"The pagers functioned perfectly for
OL,14,Fsix months," Mr Magnier said,
OL,15,Fsuggesting that an error message sent
OL,16,Fto all the devices triggered the
OL,17,Fexplosion.
